RequestTradesResult(TimeZoneInfo, ThreadSafeAccumulationList<TradeData>, Task, int?)

Creates an instance with the reference to accumulation list. This list is filled in parallel When the calling side use Items to enumerate all received items a special enumeration proxy running, which synchronizes enumeration process with filling process. As a result, enumeration will end only when filling ends
